.\" Man page for lmm status
.TH LMM-STATUS 1 "2026-01-29" "lmm" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lmm status \- Show current status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lmm status
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show configured games, active profiles, and mod counts. With \fB--game\fR, show
details for a single game (paths, profiles, mod counts).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-g ", " \-\-game\fR=ID
Show status for a specific game only.
.TP
.BR \-\-json
Output as JSON.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lmm (1),
.BR lmm-list (1).
